[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Revert the broken “early return” patch and restore the original function‐closing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the extra lines added by the last patch:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     d->count = tcount;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     return;[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restore the single `d->count = tcount;` and `return;` immediately before the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfinal `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` of `exif_mnote_data_apple_load`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strengthen the bounds‐check inside the main entry‐processing loop  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `libexif/apple/exif-mnote-data-apple.c`, locate the loop around lines [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m124[0m[39m:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < tcount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         … [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdsize > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             dofs = d->offset + [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf + ofs + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, d->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         else[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             dofs = ofs + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* OLD GUARD – too weak and only checks dofs against buf_size *[0m[35m/[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmd->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"ExifMnoteApplet"[0m[39m,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"Tag size overflow detected [0m[32m([0m[32m%u vs size %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      dofs, buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             continue;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         …[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Delete that old `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m120[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m124[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and insert [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstead:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      * Ensure that the [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mdofs .. dofs + dsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m region lies within buf[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      * This also avoids integer‐wrap. [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size || dsize > buf_size - dofs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmd->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  [0m[32m"ExifMnoteDataApple"[0m[39m,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  [0m[32m"Tag data past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32moffset %u + size %u > buffer %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  dofs, dsize, buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         continue;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Leave the following code intact:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ofs += [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     d->entries[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.data = [0m[1;35mexif_mem_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmd->mem, dsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!d->entries[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmd->log, [0m[32m"ExifMnoteApple"[0m[39m, dsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         continue;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39md->entries[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.data, buf + dofs, dsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     d->entries[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.size = dsize;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserve final bookkeeping  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After the `for` loop, ensure you have exactly:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     d->count = tcount;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     return;[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This guarantees `d` and `tcount` are in scope, no mismatched braces occur, and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe function compiles cleanly.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Test & verify  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild the library and re‐run the `exif_from_data_fuzzer` under [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that no heap‐buffer‐overflow is reported in `exif_get_sshort`, and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat all existing tests and harnesses still pass.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExplanation:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By checking `dofs > buf_size || dsize > buf_size - dofs`, we guarantee that any [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubsequent `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf + dofs, dsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` cannot walk past `buf + buf_size`, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminating the one‐byte overflow.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This mirrors the robust strategy in the Fuji loader [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich uses `CHECKOVERFLOW`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut uses a simple arithmetic check to avoid introducing new macros or dependencies.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch avoids any changes to harness code, external libraries, or tests; it [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly touches the Apple MakerNote loader and keeps its closing structure intact so [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat `d` and `tcount` remain valid when assigned.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue was an AddressSanitizer-detected heap-buffer-overflow triggered [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby the `exif_from_data_fuzzer`. The crash occurs in `exif_get_sshort` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcalled via [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_get_short`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m while parsing MakerNote entries in [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/libexif/apple/exif-mnote-data-apple.c`. The patch attempt added a guard [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst reading past the end of the buffer by checking both the data offset [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`dofs`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and the data size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`dsize`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m against `buf_size`, and updated the log [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmessage. After applying the patch and rerunning the fuzzer, the same [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow still occurs at the same location in `exif_get_sshort`, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the overflow is not addressed by the added check.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Running `exif_from_data_fuzzer` on a crafted input triggers:  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ==[0m[1;36m14[0m[39m==ERROR: AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow on address [0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[39m at pc [0m[33m...[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min exif_get_sshort[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     READ of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m at [0m[1;36m0x515000000785[0m[39m thread T0[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     #[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[39m in exif_get_sshort [0m[35m/src/libexif/libexif/[0m[95mexif-utils.c[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     #[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[39m in exif_get_short [0m[35m/src/libexif/libexif/[0m[95mexif-utils.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m104:10[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     #[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[39m in exif_mnote_data_apple_load [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/src/libexif/libexif/apple/[0m[95mexif-mnote-data-apple.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m110:29[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[33m...[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m0x515000000785[0m[39m is located [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m bytes after [0m[1;36m512[0m[39m-byte region [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x515000000580[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x515000000780[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     allocated by thread T0 here:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       #[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m malloc[0m[33m...[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     SUMMARY: AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow exif-utils.c in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_get_sshort[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash stack shows the code reading a [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte value via `exif_get_short` at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man offset beyond the buffer. The buffer in question is [0m[1;36m512[0m[39m bytes, and the read [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs at byte [0m[1;36m517[0m[39m.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Important Observations  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow is detected in the Apple MakerNote parser [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`exif_mnote_data_apple_load`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not in the fuzzer harness itself.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The original code only checked `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before proceeding to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread `dsize` bytes; it did not verify that `dofs + dsize` remained within [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`buf_size`.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The offending read happens before any later bounds checks or within a loop [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mover entries, leading to unchecked reads of the data area.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Location: `libexif/apple/exif-mnote-data-apple.c`, around line [0m[1;36m117[0m[39m in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_mnote_data_apple_load`.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original check:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag size overflow detected [0m[32m([0m[32m%u vs size %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, dofs, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         continue;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched check:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdofs > buf_size || dsize > buf_size - dofs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m,[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[32m"Tag data past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32moffset %u + size %u > buffer %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           dofs, dsize, buf_size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         continue;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch both adds `dsize > buf_size - dofs` to prevent overflow when `dofs +[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdsize` exceeds `buf_size` and renames the log context to `[0m[32m"ExifMnoteDataApple"[0m[39m`.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Result After Patch  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-running the fuzzer yields the same heap-buffer-overflow at exactly the same[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_get_sshort` in `exif-utils.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash report shows identical address ranges and stack trace, indicating [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe patch did not prevent the out-of-bounds read.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The code in `exif_mnote_data_apple_load` that computes `dofs` and `dsize` and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterates over tag entries—particularly the logic before and after the added [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck—to ensure all multi-byte reads [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. calls to `exif_get_short`, [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_get_long`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are guarded by accurate bounds checks.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The implementation of `exif_get_sshort` and `exif_get_short` in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/libexif/exif-utils.c` to understand their assumptions about buffer sizes. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any other parsing paths in `exif-data-load` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., different maker note [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformats[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that might exhibit similar missing or incorrect bounds validation.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root-cause fix or speculative cause analysis is included here; this report [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimply outlines the observed behavior, the patch attempt, and the fact that the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow persists in the same code region.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
